{"DOXOLOGICAL":[{"def":"Pertaining to doxology; giving praise to God.","pos":""}],"DOXOLOGIZE":[{"def":"To give glory to God, as in a doxology; to praise God with doxologies.","pos":""}],"DOXOLOGY":[{"def":"In Christian worship: A hymn expressing praise and honor to God; a form of praise to God designed to be sung or chanted by the choir or the congregation.","pos":""}],"DOXY":[{"def":"A loose wench; a disreputable sweetheart.","pos":""}]}